reviews.review_text: Good Golly! Thanx Russ.  I used yo have tapes of these shows...  I got to attend this first run at Shoreline.  The sound is okay, and the show pretty standard.  Short 1st set with a punchy Jack Straw opener and nice readings of High Time and Desolation Row.  My only Blue Dress>Miss Molly and this one is full of life.  I wished they would have kept it.  Estimated has a moment or two and moves quickly into a fast and short Eyes.  The Fantasy really gets going.  Peace
